flowchart TD
  U[User] -->|instructions| A[Agent runtime
(Claude Code / Cursor / Copilot)]

  subgraph Hooks[Client Hooks]
    HS[SessionStart hook
(inject routing rules)]
    PT[PreToolUse hook
(detect high-output tools)]
    PO[PostToolUse hook
(record events)]
    PC[PreCompact hook
(prevent raw dump)]
  end

  A --> HS
  A --> PT

  PT -->|route| CM[MCP Server: Context Mode]

  subgraph Sandbox[Sandbox tools]
    CE[ctx_execute / ctx_execute_file]
    CB[ctx_batch_execute]
    CI[ctx_index]
    CS[ctx_search]
    CF[ctx_fetch_and_index]
  end

  CM --> CE --> T1[External tools
(shell, web fetch, file reads, etc.)]
  T1 -->|raw output| CE
  CE -->|small structured summary + artifact id| A

  PO --> CM
  CM -->|append events| DB[(SQLite event log)]
  DB -->|FTS5 index| IDX[(FTS5)]
  CS -->|BM25 query| IDX
  IDX -->|relevant snippets| CS --> A

  PC -->|compaction happens| A
  A -->|no raw tool output re-injected| A
